commit.message:
feat: Custom persister support

* feat: Custom persister support

* Create a @pollyjs/persister package
* Move out shared utils into their own @pollyjs/utils package
* Add support to register a custom persister (same way as an adapter)
* Add more tests

* docs: Custom adapter & persister docs

* test: Add custom persister test

docs: General doc fixes. (#3)

* docs: Minor changes.

* docs: Update travis-ci badge to point at the public site.
docs: Reorder how the docs are laid out.
docs: Improve "Getting Started" docs + add package READMEs.
chore: Add more details to all package.json files.
refactor: Rewrite test-helpers to eliminate FIFO hook ordering.
refactor(ember): Move server options to its own object.
